title: NFL Week 3 recap
itunes:title: NFL Week 3 recap
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- recap all of the Week 3 action and debate on which teams will have a winning season. The crew also breaks down the Super Bowl XLVIII rematch between the Denver Broncos and Seattle Seahawks and the Sunday Night Football matchup between the Pittsburgh Steelers and Carolina Panthers.
